Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:16.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:24.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}話しても　まだまだ　足りないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:31.54,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夕焼けが　街を染めてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:38.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うように　なかなか　いかない…って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:46.63,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}気づいたら　一緒に　泣いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:50.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}恋も　夢も　花も　虹も　風も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:53.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ぜんぶ掴もうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:56.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　元気出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:01.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:08.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今日のミス　悔やむより　今　乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　迷わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:17.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まだ見ぬ未来へと向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:22.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっと　歩いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:25.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Dear My Friend every day & night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:29.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:24.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}話還遠遠沒有說夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:31.54,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}晚霞已染紅了街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:38.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}世事難都如人願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:46.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}察覺時已相依哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:50.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}戀情  夢想  鮮花  彩虹  微風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:53.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}抓緊這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:56.98,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:01.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為有我在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:08.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}與其悔恨今日不如放眼明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  不要迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:17.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向著未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:22.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}永遠走下去
